title: MAM Easy Start™ self-sterilising bottle: safe and so practical
description:
Discover MAM Easy Start bottle, the ideal baby bottle for newborns – for an easy switch between breastfeeding and bottle.
Thanks to its wide openings and its removable base, filling and cleaning are especially easy. 
The unique self-sterilising function ensures simple, safe bottle cleaning, in only 3 minutes in the microwave with 20ml of water: this feature is not only innovative but also exceptionally handy for on-the-go!
